线性表上的最大独立集问题。动态规划解决。

$$
d_i=\max(d_{i-1},d_{i-2}+v_i)
$$

```python
class Solution:
    def rob(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        l = len(nums)
        if l == 0:
            return 0
        elif l == 1:
            return nums[0]

        dp = [0]*l
        dp[0] = nums[0]
        dp[1] = max(nums[0], nums[1])
        for i in range(2, l):
            dp[i] = max(dp[i-1], dp[i-2]+nums[i])
        return max(dp)
```
